Custos Sharing Registry Service

To start the service go to org.apache.custos.sharing.service.api and run Application.java

Following are the list of APIs along with sample request body. Please please replace host and port number according to the host and port on which sharing registry service is running.

##Domain

To get all domains
GET http://localhost:7070/domains?offset=%d&limit=%d

Create a new domain
POST http://localhost:7070/domains
{
	"domainId": "test-domain",
	"name": "test-domain"
}

Update a domain
PUT http://localhost:7070/domains
{
	"domainId": "test-domain",
	"name": "test-domain",
	"description":"updating the description"
}

Check if domain exists
HEAD http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}

To retrieve a domain
GET http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}

To delete a domain
DELETE http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}

##Users

Get all users is a domain
GET http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}/users?offset=%d&limit=%d

Create a new user in a domain
http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}/users
{
	"userId": "user1",
	"domainId": "domain",
	"userName": "test-user"
}

Update a user in a domain
PUT http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}/users
{
	"userId": "user1",
	"domainId": "domain",
	"userName": "test-user"
}

Check if a user exists in a domain
GET http://localhost:7070/domains/domain/users/user1

Delete a user is a domain
DELETE http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}/users/{userId}

Get a user
GET http://localhost:7070/domains/{domainId}/users/{userId}



